title: 642. 5 Takeaways from Championship Sunday
itunes:title: 642. 5 Takeaways from Championship Sunday
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick fives storylines that stood out from Championship Sunday in a special new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys discuss the Tampa Bay Buccaneers aggressive play style in a win over the Green Bay Packers (:55). Next, they look at the Green Bay Packers late game decisions (9:05). Later, the trio explain why the Kansas City Chiefs are no longer bored after their dominant win over the Buffalo Bills (15:08). Then, they talk about the Buffalo Bills and why field goals won't beat the Kansas City Chiefs (21:21). To wrap up the show, the guys preview the Super Bowl matchup between the Kansas City Chiefs and Tampa Bay Buccaneers (29:29). All that and more in this packed episode. Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
